8) Why Non-IT to IT?

ЁЯСЙ Final Answer:

I shifted from non-IT to IT because I genuinely enjoy technology and problem-solving. My non-IT background helped me build logical thinking and discipline. IT gives me continuous learning opportunities and allows me to grow both technically and professionally.

